               <p>On the 9th of November last, I was in <placeName id="t17851214-18-crimeloc105">Cheapside</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17851214-18-crimeloc105" type="placeName" value="Cheapside"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17851214-18-crimeloc105" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851214-18-off103 t17851214-18-crimeloc105"></join>, at one o'clock; I saw the prisoner take a handkerchief out of a gentleman's pocket near the corner of Queen-street, I immediately took the prisoner with the handkerchief in his pocket; being Lord Mayor's day, and the mob being so great, I could not get up to the gentleman.</p>
               <p>Court. What are you? - I am warder of Cheap ward.</p>
